Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:22.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(0,300)}在這過於廣大的世界一隅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:28.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(0,800)}心靈融化掉
